title: Ground News - Ministry of Labor: We have provided jobs for 553,170 young people, including 10,000 people of concern during 2023
text:
Summary by اليوم السابع On Friday, the Ministry of Labor publishes an “infographic” showing the Ministry's efforts to provide services to citizens during the year 2023. The directives of President Abdel Fattah El-Sisi were and still are a road map for the Ministry. Source: Today 7 Ministry of Labor: We have provided jobs for 553 thousand and 170 young people, including 10 thousand people of concern during 2023 Share menu More
